	1.	Same branch ‚Üí rhetorical / linguistic devices that manage meaning, noise, and compression (metaphor‚Äôs cousins)
	2.	Different domains ‚Üí non-linguistic mechanisms that do the same job (coordinate meaning under uncertainty)

